{"id":8782,"date":"2020-06-15T10:29:24","date_gmt":"2020-06-15T10:29:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=8782"},"modified":"2022-10-11T14:18:50","modified_gmt":"2022-10-11T07:18:50","slug":"cai-tao-noi-that-chung-cu-cu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/cai-tao-noi-that-chung-cu-cu\/","title":{"rendered":"B\u1eaeT TAY C\u1ea2I T\u1ea0O N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T CHUNG C\u01af C\u0168 C\u1ea6N L\u01afU \u00dd NH\u1eeeNG G\u00cc?"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<p>Sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t chung c\u01b0 b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea5p, phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p th\u1eddi; ho\u1eb7c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 mua l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e0ng m\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh,&#8230;ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o chung c\u01b0 c\u0169. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1, li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1, nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 bao g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u0103n h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea7n li\u00ean k\u1ebft chung. Do \u0111\u00f3, khi c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o, s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 xung quanh. Sau \u0111\u00e2y <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/Byzannoithathiendai\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan<\/a> s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n ghi nh\u1edb khi c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t chung c\u01b0 c\u0169 \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 m\u01a1.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>N\u1eafm b\u1eaft m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 c\u0169\u00a0<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 hi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 c\u0169 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 t\u1eebng h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c trong b\u1ea3n v\u1ebd m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea1ng. B\u1edfi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o v\u00ec s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u to\u00e0n chung c\u01b0.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-12036\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/z3683481297395_0eac961326df9b2549f7adf61e7b49eb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"938\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/z3683481297395_0eac961326df9b2549f7adf61e7b49eb.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/z3683481297395_0eac961326df9b2549f7adf61e7b49eb-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/z3683481297395_0eac961326df9b2549f7adf61e7b49eb-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/z3683481297395_0eac961326df9b2549f7adf61e7b49eb-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u gia \u0111\u00ecnh khi s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 c\u0169 mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc khu b\u1ebfp, nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tho\u00e1t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, khi c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eadp b\u1ecf c\u00e1c c\u1ed9t d\u1ea7m ch\u00ednh, b\u1edfi n\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u chung c\u01b0.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>L\u00ean b\u1ea3n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi ti\u1ebft c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o, s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>L\u00ean b\u1ea3n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi ti\u1ebft c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng gi\u00fap tr\u00e1nh thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed thi c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" class=\"wp-image-8787\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/plan.jpg\" alt=\"cai-tao-chung-cu-cu\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/plan.jpg 800w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/plan-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/plan-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\r\n<figcaption><em>Li\u1ec7t k\u00ea chi ti\u1ebft c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/em><\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o chung c\u01b0 c\u0169, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o v\u00e0 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. H\u00e3y ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng v\u00e0 li\u1ec7t k\u00ea chi ti\u1ebft t\u1eebng h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c t\u1eeb tr\u1ea7n, s\u00e0n, t\u01b0\u1eddng,&#8230;Li\u1ec7t k\u00ea c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u chi ph\u00ed hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o thi\u1ebfu h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>T\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i uy t\u00edn, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>C\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o chung c\u01b0 c\u0169 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, h\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e2u n\u0103m trong ng\u00e0nh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ph\u00ed trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thi c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m t\u1ed1i \u0111a th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\">\r\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12038\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/183-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/183-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/183-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/183-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/183-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/183-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/183-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/p>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft tay h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n n\u00ean g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 n\u1eafm r\u00f5 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n chi ph\u00ed c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kinh ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>N\u00eau r\u00f5 nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 n\u1ebfp s\u1ed1ng, n\u1ebfp sinh ho\u1ea1t, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u00ec v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c n\u00eau r\u00f5 nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u00fap ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 mang t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec7n nghi, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gu th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" class=\"wp-image-8789\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/3-3-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"cai-tao-chung-cu-cu\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/3-3-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/3-3-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/3-3-768x480.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/3-3-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-